{{2022 Atlantic Coast Conference football standings}}

The '''2022 Atlantic Coast Conference football season''', part of the [[2022 NCAA Division I FBS football season]], was the 70th season of [[college football]] played for the [[Atlantic Coast Conference]] (ACC). The ACC consisted of 14 members in two divisions. The entire schedule was released on January 31, 2022.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theacc.com/news/2022-acc-football-schedule-set-to-be-revealed-exclusively-on-acc-network-january-31|title=2022 ACC Football Schedule Set To Be Revealed Exclusively On ACC Network January 31, 2022|website=TheACC.com|date=January 25, 2022|accessdate=January 25, 2022}}{{Dead link|date=July 2023 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> This was the last season that the conference used divisions in its football scheduling.

